{"tid":307264,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【力威胡師傅】解構「俾啲掙扎」的意義 「唔掙扎同條死魚有咩分別」","createTime":"2017-07-03T08:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T10:14:01.000Z","uid":29609,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce2678f0a2636091c672963f7c9793c9b3a4c94d","tid":307264,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170628/large/1498642750_fb27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498642750_fb27.jpg&h=f9050678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2017/07/01/98903_20170701114643_59571b23f2a24.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F98903_20170701114643_59571b23f2a24.gif&h=4c119067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2017/07/01/98905_20170701114722_59571b4af03dd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F98905_20170701114722_59571b4af03dd.gif&h=a3e37038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2017/07/01/98902_20170701114628_59571b1465d00.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F98902_20170701114628_59571b1465d00.gif&h=f9d7ff76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2017/04/03/73110_20170403023855_58e1453f25fd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F03%2F73110_20170403023855_58e1453f25fd4.gif&h=b684e7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170702/2_524100_0/-%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E8%83%A1%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%85-%E8%A7%A3%E6%A7%8B-%E4%BF%BE%E5%95%B2%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E-%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9-%E5%94%94%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E%E5%90%8C%E6%A2%9D%E6%AD%BB%E9%AD%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170702%2F2_524100_0%2F-%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2582%2585-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25A7%258B-%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E5%2595%25B2%25E6%258E%2599%25E6%2589%258E-%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9-%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%258E%2599%25E6%2589%258E%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25AD%259A%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%25A9%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%2588%25A5-&d=qkH9MG4TnKNvQhBVOrBuADPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0ccea601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170702%2F2_524100_0%2F-%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2582%2585-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25A7%258B-%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E5%2595%25B2%25E6%258E%2599%25E6%2589%258E-%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9-%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%258E%2599%25E6%2589%258E%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25AD%259A%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%25A9%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%2588%25A5-&h=38167552\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170702/2_524100_0/-%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E8%83%A1%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%85-%E8%A7%A3%E6%A7%8B-%E4%BF%BE%E5%95%B2%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E-%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9-%E5%94%94%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E%E5%90%8C%E6%A2%9D%E6%AD%BB%E9%AD%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5-</a><br />\n「俾啲掙扎！！！」力威健身學院創辦人胡力威師傅訓徒時的一句口頭禪，竟意外地成為了時下年輕人經常掛在口邊的潮語，胡師傅也因而為了網絡紅人。 <br />\n<br />\n胡師傅於一九九三年成立力威健身學院，強調健身也健心。「健身與健心，健心反而更重要，因為健身一段時間就可以成功，但健心可為你帶來正能量，以生命影響生命。」不少網民都知道，胡師傅在指導愛徒操肌時，很愛說「俾啲掙扎」，原來所謂的掙扎，並不僅僅是指肌肉上的掙扎，還指心靈上的。 <br />\n<br />\n他形容道：「掙扎才是真正的訓練，一定要在個過程中掙扎，你不掙扎，肌肉細胞不會有深層的撕破，沒有深層的撕破，就不會得到肌肉。人生也一樣，沒有掙扎的話，和街市的死魚沒兩樣。人生、心靈上都要掙扎，真的，不掙扎不強大。」"},{"pid":"2c6ff22ebb22a432d0fd9ca38ed33cbaa48aa7ea","tid":307264,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://beta.ziines.com/files/getFile?fileKey=58e12f05bf2fe&amp;param=4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeta.ziines.com%2Ffiles%2FgetFile%3FfileKey%3D58e12f05bf2fe%26param%3D4&h=59ad848b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a8425694cb9776af2a1829d34415ccd4a42f31f","tid":307264,"uid":232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"胡師父教春麗操腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要操腳架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e5ab8644fcc01469c8cf2f9c3bb2640ecd75c1","tid":307264,"uid":65376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胡師父教春麗操腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要操腳架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nj腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f075c8b072fcc7c9594ea7e9fb7e8e3fd643b1d4","tid":307264,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胡師父教春麗操腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要操腳架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n春麗出名腳粗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9c26a3111cae65ceaffba7b6186c37d0efe8a0","tid":307264,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"連登啲胡師父仲未入嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7008a4cff75b2bf03b717c5de33e4a10404e7f5","tid":307264,"uid":99355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登啲胡師父仲未入嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日d 堂full晒 ， 太忙啦"},{"pid":"1201ffb2ad0b861d7c2ecf9ed3e659463d901e77","tid":307264,"uid":99355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"各位季候鳥都要比D 掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02caaf6cf174c69e946e22c6da0aa783c973dc7","tid":307264,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:11:26.000Z","msg":"但飲奶粉係咩一回事"},{"pid":"278b0040ba02ee9ab44f2667db618a62d5d7146c","tid":307264,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但飲奶粉係咩一回事</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170703/2_524106_0/-%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E8%83%A1%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%85-%E8%AB%96%E7%9B%A1%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E5%A3%9E%E9%A2%A8%E6%B0%A3-%E9%A3%B2%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%83%E8%85%8E%E8%99%A7%E7%94%A9%E9%A0%AD%E9%AB%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170703%2F2_524106_0%2F-%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2582%2585-%25E8%25AB%2596%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%2581%25A5%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25A3%259E%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E7%25B2%2589%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2585%258E%25E8%2599%25A7%25E7%2594%25A9%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%25AB%25AE&d=qkH9MG4TnKNvQhBVOrBuADPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6929ac82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170703%2F2_524106_0%2F-%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2582%2585-%25E8%25AB%2596%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%2581%25A5%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25A3%259E%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E7%25B2%2589%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2585%258E%25E8%2599%25A7%25E7%2594%25A9%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%25AB%25AE&h=62aeb168\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170703/2_524106_0/-%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E8%83%A1%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%85-%E8%AB%96%E7%9B%A1%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E5%A3%9E%E9%A2%A8%E6%B0%A3-%E9%A3%B2%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%83%E8%85%8E%E8%99%A7%E7%94%A9%E9%A0%AD%E9%AB%AE</a><br />\n【力威胡師傅】論盡健身壞風氣 飲太多奶粉會腎虧甩頭髮<br />\n<br />\n力威，力大如牛、威猛如虎，是一個光聽就足以震攝人的名字，不過，力威健身學院創辦人胡力威在小時候卻十分瘦弱。為何胡師傅會踏上健身之路，要由小時侯說起。<span style=\"color: red;\">年幼的胡師傅身體孱弱，身高近六呎，卻只有一百二十磅重，還經常受耳鳴和頭暈困擾，屢次求醫不果。他憶述，當年他針灸的地方對面有一所健力學院（舊式健身中心）：「當時心想不如做做運動，看看會否好一點，後來覺得好點了，就繼續下去。」 </span><br />\n<br />\n「拿張外國人的相，告訴你練完就可以變成這樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">飲了大隻仔奶粉吸收了蛋白質就會變大隻變靚，其實不是，吸收太多蛋白質對肝腎不也好，也容易脫髮，皮膚變差。</span>健美比賽並不是健身的終極目標，健身的終極目標，是靠運動和維持良好生活習慣，把自己潛在的完美體態迫出來，而不應靠打針食藥。」 <br />\n<br />\n胡師傅於一九九三年成立標榜「健身健心」的力威健身學院，縱橫健身界三十餘年，見盡健身運動的起起落落，有些事件他不吐不快。「現在的健身風氣很差，特別是近十年八載。」<span style=\"color: red;\">他發現今時今日有很多商人利用健身行騙，旨在哄騙消費者購買包裝得五花八門的健身療程，又拚命推銷客人飲外國奶粉：「他們只要你消費，療程有沒有作用並不重要，最緊要碌爆你張卡，或者隨便教，盡量等客人自己做，慳水慳力，留精力教下一個。」 </span>"}]}